  "description": "<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://a2.att.hudong.com/75/62/01200000030711136358625188702.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 233px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p705276\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\tMauricio Pochettino has been appointed as the new coach of Tottenham Hotspur on a five-year <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/contract\" target=\"_blank\">contract</a>. The Argentine replaces Tim Sherwood who was sacked a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fortnight\" target=\"_blank\">fortnight</a> ago. BBC's sport reporter David Ornstein has more.</p>\n<p>\n\tHe brings with him all of his coaching <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/staff\" target=\"_blank\">staff</a> from Southampton who were also his coaching staff at Espanyol. He was at <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Southampton\" target=\"_blank\">Southampton</a> since January 2013. He led the club to eighth in the Premier League last season. And he's really been known for that attacking, attractive style of football. But huge question marks now remain for Southampton. What will happen to their players such as Luke Shaw and Adam Lallana? Will there be an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/exodus\" target=\"_blank\">exodus</a>?</p>\n<p>\n\tIn a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/statement\" target=\"_blank\">statement</a>, the Tottenham Chairman Daniel Levy said &quot;In Mauricio I believe we have a head coach who, with his high-energy, attacking football, will embrace the style of play we <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/associate\" target=\"_blank\">associate</a> with our club. He has proved an ability to develop each player as an individual whilst building a great team-spirit and a winning-mentality.&quot;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span>声明：音视频均来自互联网链接，仅供学习使用。本网站自身