  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/c28f6ed441d84c13acf7cc6a9db85cd1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t还在羡慕BBC播音员员一口地道标准的英式发音吗？想要练就纯正英音，《BBC英音模仿秀》帮你忙！《BBC英音模仿秀》是一档沪江部落的原创口语互动节目，主持人对音频进行重点讲解和示范模仿，并对大家递交的口语模仿作品进行一对一的点评！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/2120/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/7e2a59a999f44c92a141bbeff7458379.jpg\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>今日主持人：Junekaname</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>22秒音频： </strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p704490\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>主持人模仿音频： </strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p704490\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>模仿文本：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t\tIn my search for understanding the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/motivation\" target=\"_blank\">motivation</a> of those who joined the race to produce the bomb whose use at Hiroshima and Nagasaki <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/appal\" target=\"_blank\">appal</a>led the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/world\" target=\"_blank\">world</a>, I eventually decided to turn from fact to fiction. If historians could not fill the gaps in the record that made the knowledge I was after so <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/elusive\" target=\"_blank\">elusive</a>, perhaps storytellers less shackled by documented evidence might do so.</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<strong>语调示意图：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201409/1fe47fb3-241e-42ed-83ac-c0b493f14e4b.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>重点单词发音讲解：</strong><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n\tmotivation<br />\n\tappal<br />\n\tworld</