  "description": "<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8em;\">noticeable.</span><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Deja vu\" target=\"_blank\">Deja vu</a><br />\n\tPeople sometimes experience a situation for the first time, but they feel like they have already experienced it before. This feeling of deja vu can be interesting. What is the person doing when he or she encounters deja vu? Does the person recall the outcome of the deja vu? Does the actual event have the same outcome as the deja vu, or does it turn out differently?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: This feels like deja vu... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWhen he popped the last bite of the sandwich into his mouth, Wolfe saw the editor step away from the crowd. He quickly rushed in front of the editor and handed him the document. While waiting for the document to be read and signed, Wolfe glanced back and saw the photo shoot had started. The model caught his attention immediately. That <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/piercing\" target=\"_blank\">piercing</a> stare, the intensity, I do feel like I've seen him somewhere before. The product being promoted also caught his eye. In the shape of an &ldquo;L,&rdquo; the clear glass bottle was filled with a liquid with a black <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/tint\" target=\"_blank\">tint</a>. I wonder what that <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cologne\" target=\"_blank\">cologne</a> smells like.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/15844851156/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p704489/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p704489\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706212/\">外媒看中国 为什么中国光棍这么多</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706120/\">爱恨已入土 安妮斯顿称不再恨皮特夫妇</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706266/\">大跌眼镜 英媒评出最具影响力的10本书</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706222/\">互有利弊 茶和咖啡谁更健康</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p626570/\">面试官才不会告诉你这10件事呢</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706246/\">我是剧透狗 美国队长3泄密剧情盘点</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p705983/\">囧研究 男女都喜欢单性办公室</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p705984/\">囧研究 4成男人故意做不好家务</a></li><li style=\"marg